definition: car/vehicle/CL:輛|辆[liang4]/machine/to shape with a lathe/Kangxi radical 159

sentences.english: Is there any information from Moon rover, what was seen on moon?
sentences.chinese: 月球車是否傳回任何信息，能看到月球上的什麼嗎？

sentences.english: The spaceman will drive his moon car around to study the moon .
sentences.chinese: 宇航員將開着月球車到處考察月球。

sentences.english: A Chandrayaan-2 rover is planned for 2011.
sentences.chinese: “月船二號”月球車計劃在2011年研發出來。

sentences.english: By the behavior control method, the rover navigates autonomously.
sentences.chinese: 運用行爲控制方法實現月球車的自主導航。

sentences.english: First they unlocked the rover wheels, thendisconnected the cable to the lander.
sentences.chinese: 首先他們解鎖月球車的車輪，接着斷開着陸器纜繩。
